当前Flash Player已停止更新，并于2021年1月12日封锁Flash内容。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Adobe Flash Player EOL General Information Page|url=https://www.adobe.com/products/flashplayer/end-of-life.html|accessdate=2021-01-06|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2017-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170205181300/http://www.adobe.com/aboutadobe/pressroom/pressreleases/200708/082107FlashPlayer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而中国大陆将仍然由重橙网络科技代理，不受任何影响。另有非官方以[[Rust|Rust]]製作Flash Player的模擬器[[Ruffle|Ruffle]]，以便延續使用原本的Flash應用程式。<ref>{{cite web |title=Ruffle - Flash Player emulator written in the Rust programming language |url=https://ruffle.rs/ |accessdate=2021-01-15 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126040413/https://ruffle.rs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

